text: Alison Jane Williamson is a retired archer from Great Britain. She was born on 3 November 1971. Williamson competed at the 1992, 1996, 2000, 2004, 2008, and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Alison WilliamsonAlison WILLIAMSON == References == Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:British archers Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Great Britain Category:Sportspeople from Leicestershire
